      <title>KKR 将以 27 亿美元收购 Global Atlantic 保险公司的其余部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/kkr-to-pay-2-7-billion-for-the-rest-of-insurer-global-atlantic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR&amp; Co. 将支付约 27 亿美元现金，收购其尚未拥有的 Global Atlantic 剩余 37% 的股份，扩大其在保险领域的赌注，以推动资产和费用增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/kkr-to-pay-2-7-billion-for-the-rest-of-insurer-global-atlantic</guid>
